Would you follow Jimmy Chin @jimmychin knowing he’s one of the only people to ever ski off the summit of Mount Everest? 

14 brave and lucky customers enjoyed the first ever US-based experience with this Panerai Ambassador in Jackson Hole, Wyoming, where Jimmy resides for much of the year.

It’s been the perfect occasion to get an insider view on his life through outdoor adventures, including climbing and wakeboarding, sharing in his favorite pastimes and top dining destinations as well as discovering the most prized pieces from his Panerai collection:
